-india-to-china%2Farticleshow%2F102734001.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22During%20the%2019th%20round%20of%20military%20talks%2C%20India%20asked%20China%20to%20withdraw%20forward%20deployed%20troops%20and%20restore%20Indian%20soldiers'%20patrolling%20rights%20in%20Depsang%20Plains%20and%20Demchok%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh.%20The%20talks%20ended%20much%20earlier%20than%20usual%2C%20but%20the%20official%20outcome%20has%20not%20been%20disclosed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22RAJAT%20PANDIT%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Frestore-our-patrol-rights-india-to-china%2Farticleshow%2F102734001.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20fierce%20naval%20battle%2035%20years%20ago%20shows%20how%20destructive%20another%20US%20showdown%20with%20Iran%20could%20get%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20Navy%20Persian%20Gulf%20tanker%20convoy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64da5f5f5e5d5a00195d999e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Navy%20guided-missile%20frigate%20USS%20Hawes%20leads%20a%20reflagged%20tanker%20and%20two%20US%20warships%20in%20a%20convoy%20in%20the%20Persian%20Gulf%20in%20October%201987.%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%2FPH2%20Elliot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20military%20is%20sending%20forces%20to%20the%20Persian%20Gulf%20in%20response%20to%20Iran's%20seizure%20of%20oil%20tankers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20deployments%20have%20been%20compared%20to%20a%20US%20operation%20in%201987-1988%20to%20defend%20tankers%20from%20Iranian%20attacks.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EToday%2C%20however%2C%20Iran%20fields%20a%20much%20different%20military%2C%20and%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20Gulf%20has%20changed%2C%20experts%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3ETensions%20are%20rising%20in%20the%20P