%20ability%20to%20comment%20on%20songs%20and%20react%20to%20what%20other%20users%20are%20saying.%20This%20sets%20it%20apart%20from%20leading%20streamers%20like%20Spotify%20and%20Apple%20Music%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2023%2F01%2F31%2Fspotifys-test-of-a-friends-tab-on-mobile-hints-at-expanded-social-ambitions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20limited%20in-app%20social%20features%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20find%20in%20our%20consumer%20surveys%20that%20younger%20consumers%20are%20more%20interested%20in%20having%20a%20more%20social%20streaming%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Tatiana%20Cirisano%2C%20a%20music-industry%20analyst%20and%20consultant%20at%20the%20research%20firm%20MIDiA%20Research%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BSpotify%20is%20starting%20to%20offer%20more%20things%20in%20that%20vein%2C%20but%20I%20just%20see%20it%20as%20an%20opportunity%20that's%20ripe%20for%20TikTok's%20taking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20may%20also%20be%20uniquely%20positioned%20to%20capture%20younger%20users%20as%20they%20start%20to%20enter%20the%20marketplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they've%20grown%20up%20with%20TikTok%20before%20they%20are%20actually%20spending%20money%20on%20any%20subscriptions%2C%20and%20then%20TikTok%20Music%20is%20out%20there%2C%20that%20could%20be%20pretty%20scary%20for%20Spotify%20and%20some%20of%20these%20other%20players%20if%20they're%20thinking%20about%20the%20next%20generation%2C%26quot%3B%20Cirisano%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20still%20very%20early%20days%20for%20TikTok%20Music%2C%20and%20its%20rivals%20have%20a%20big%20headstart%20%E2%80%94%20Apple%20Music%20and%20Spotify%20are%20each%20in%20more%20than%20100%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20other%20relative%20newcomers%20like%20YouTube%20Music%20have%20shown%20there's%20room%20to%20break%20into%20music%20streaming%2C%20particularly%20for%20platforms%20that%20can%20leverage%20another%20popular%20app%20to%20drive%20sign-ups.%20YouTube%20reached%2073%20million%20music%20subscriptions%20in%20Q4%202022%2C%20up%20from%2023%20million%20three%20years%20earlier%2C%20per%20data%20compiled%20by%20MIDiA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20has%20not%20yet%20said%20when%20TikTok%20Music%20will%20roll%20out%20to%20other%20countries%20including%20the%20US.%20A%20spokesperson%20told%20Insider%20in%20July%20it%20will%20have%20%26quot%3Bmore%20news%20to%20share%26quot%3B%20on%20that%20front%20in%20the%20coming%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20our%20tour%20of%20the%20app%20in%20Singapore%2C%20we%20found%20TikTok%20Music%20stood%20out%20from%20its%20peers%20with%20unique%20social%20features%20and%20a%20Shazam-style%20song%20identifier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20we%20felt%20TikTok%20Music's%20%26quot%3BFor%20You%26quot%3B%20song%20recommendations%20in%20its%20discovery%20feed%20missed%20the%20mark%20%E2%80%94%20a%20surprising%20deficiency%20given%20its%20sister%20app%20is%20known%20for%20having%20an%20industry-leading%20content-recommendation%20algorithm%20%E2%80%94%20although%20the%20music%20app%20did%20excel%20at%20making%20song%20mixes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETikTok%20Music%20requires%20users%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20a%20subscription%20%E2%80%94%20and%20having%20a%20TikTok%20account%20is%20not%20optional%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshots%20of%20signup%20process%20on%20TikTok%20Music%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c8bab5048ff200190e9832%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EScreenshots%20of%20the%20TikTok%20Music%20sign-up%20process.%3Cp%3ETikTok%20Music%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EImmediately%20upon%20launch%2C%20the%20app%20prompts%20users%20to%20sign%20in%20via%20TikTok.%20We%20were%20required%20to%20have%20an%20account%20on%20the%20short-form%20video%20app%20to%20even%20use%20TikTok%20Music.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBreaking%20away%20from%20Spotify%20and%20o