20new%20songs%20versus%20hearing%20more%20familiar%20tracks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20that's%20really%20the%20only%20form%20of%20control%20a%20user%20has%20over%20the%20app's%20algorithm%2C%20as%20they%20can't%20control%20other%20factors%20like%20genre%20or%20mood.%20Users%20need%20to%20make%20their%20own%20playlists%20or%20request%20a%20%26quot%3Bsimilar%20mix%26quot%3B%20from%20a%20particular%20song%20in%20order%20to%20guarantee%20they'll%20hear%20certain%20types%20of%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20has%20a%20dedicated%20history%20page%20that%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20songs%20while%20jumping%20between%20playlists.%20It%20also%20has%20a%20built-in%20music%20identifier%20that%20can%20recognize%20songs%20playing%20around%20a%20user.%20The%20feature%20basically%20renders%20Apple-owned%20Shazam%20obsolete%20if%20this%20is%20your%20primary%20music%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20Music%20also%20has%20a%20useful%20trick%20for%20social%20gatherings%2C%20offering%20a%20party%20mode%20that%20allows%20you%20to%20pump%20up%20the%20volume%20even%20higher%20and%20to%20use%20your%20phone's%20flashlight%20function%20as%20a%20strobe%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETikTok%20puts%20a%20greater%20emphasis%20on%20social%20listening%20than%20other%20streaming%20apps%20we've%20used%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshot%20of%20TikTok%20Music's%20social%20features%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d5c18c7e9149001aa47b77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EScreenshot%20of%20TikTok%20Music's%20social%20features.%3Cp%3ETikTok%20Music%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20Music%20features%20a%20comments%20section%20for%20every%20song%2C%20reminiscent%20of%20comments%20from%20the%20main%20TikTok%20app.%20Unlike%20other%20streaming%20apps%2C%20the%20comments%20don't%20seem%20like%20an%20afterthought%20%E2%80%94%20top%20comments