-violent-incidents-list-2019-11%5C%22%3Eviolent%20incidents%20at%20Popeyes%20restaurants%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20even%20connected%20to%20customers%20trying%20to%20get%20their%20hands%20on%20the%20sandwich.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsumer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-chicken-wars-pandemic-2021-2%5C%22%3Edemand%20for%20chicken%20sandwiches%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20mounting%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20among%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-fast-food-restaurants-spicy-change-menu-2023-5%5C%22%3EGen%20Z%20consumers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20other%20fast-food%20chains%20have%20been%20clamoring%20to%20satisfy%20those%20cravings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurger%20King%2C%20Taco%20Bell%2C%20and%20KFC%20each%20launched%20their%20takes%20on%20chicken%20sandwiches%20within%20the%20last%20two%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Popeyes%20launched%20their%20chicken%20sandwich%20in%20late%202019%2C%20it%20created%20a%20lot%20of%20buzz%20and%20excitement%20that%20fueled%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20other%20brands%20to%20look%20at%20their%20own%20chicken%20platforms%20and%20make%20a%20judgment%20on%20their%20offerings%2C%26quot%3B%20Haracz%20previously%20told%20Insider%20in%202021.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20anything%20like%20that%20happens%2C%20other%20chains'%20main%20objective%20is%20to%20get%20a%20piece%20of%20that%20share.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-mcdonalds-chef-chain-chicken-sandwich-imitate-chick-fil-as-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692042456000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F603692f7bed5c50011a2c493%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-mcdonalds-chef-chain-chicken-sandwich-imitate-chick-fil-as-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20McDonald's%20chef%20shared%20some%20insight%20on%2