520questioned%2520the%2520adequacy%2Cwhich%2520was%2520set%2520in%25202008.%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ELivelaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20are%20the%20fines%20that%20you%20impose%3F%20How%20much%20does%20the%20TV%20channel%20make%20from%20an%20advertisement%20in%20one%20program%3F%20No%20TV%20channel%20has%20any%20motivation%20to%20comply%20with%20your%20self-regulatory%20mechanism%2C%20and%20if%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20violation%2C%20you%20are%20going%20to%20impose%20a%20penalty%20of%20a%20lakh%20of%20rupees%2C%20there%20you%20have%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20said%20penalties%20imposed%20on%20TV%20channels%20for%20airing%20disputed%20news%20must%20be%20proportionate%20to%20the%20profits%20earned%2C%20rather%20than%20Rs%201%20lakh%20fine%2C%20fixed%20way%20back%20in%202008.%20Only%20such%20fines%20can%20act%20as%20a%20deterrent%20for%20television%20channels%20to%20act%20with%20responsibility%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20three-judge%20bench%2C%20led%20by%20CJI%2C%20was%20hearing%20a%20petition%20by%20the%20NBDA%20challenging%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%202021%20verdict%20that%20contained%20adverse%20observations%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20teeth%20in%20the%20self-regulation%20of%20TV%20channels.%20The%20Bombay%20high%20court%20had%20held%20that%20trial%20by%20media%20interferes%20with%20the%20criminal%20investigation%20by%20police%20and%20issued%20a%20slew%20of%20directions%20to%20the%20media%20to%20be%20followed%20while%20reporting%20incidents%20involving%20suicide%20and%20death%20of%20persons.%20The%20high%20court%20was%20back%20then%20hearing%20a%20batch%20of%20petitions%20questioning%20the%20media%20trial%20in%20the%20actor%20Sushant%20Singh%20Rajput%E2%80%99s%20death%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20agreeing%20with%20the%20petitioners%E2%80%99%20contention%20that%20there%20has%20to%20be%20no%20government%20interference%20in%20regulating%20the%20media%2C%20the%20apex%20court%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20self-regulatory%20mechanism%20has%20to%20be%20effective.%20The%20CJI%20said%20it%20will%20issue%20guidelines%20to%20strengthen%20the%20regulation%20of%20TV%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692032395000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fpenalties-on-tv-channels-for-airing-disputed-news-must-be-proportionate-to-profits-says-sc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20observing%20that%20the%20current%20self-regulatory%20mechanism%20by%20News%20Broadcasters%20and%20Digital%20Association%20in%20force%20is%20not%20effective%2C%20vowing%20to%20issue%20guidelines%20to%20strengthen%20the%20regulation%20of%20TV%20channels.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fpenalties-on-tv-channels-for-airing-disputed-news-must-be-proportionate-to-profits-says-sc%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chrisley%20Family%20Attempts%20Reality%20TV%20Comeback%20While%20Todd%20and%20Julie%20Serve%20Prison%20Sentences%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692032169000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2Fchrisley-knows-best.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D526%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235695721%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Chrisley%20family%20is%20returning%20to%20television%20with%20a%20brand%20new%20unscripted%20docuseries%20from%20Scout%20Productions.%20Following%20the%20lives%20of%20Chase%2C%20Savannah%2C%20Grayson%2C%20Chloe%20and%20%E2%80%9CNanny%E2%80%9D%20Faye%20Chrisley%2C%20the%20series%20will%20pull%20back%20the%20curtain%20on%20one%20of%20the%20most%20turbulent%20times%20for%20the%20family%20since%20starring%20in%20%E2%80%9CChrisley%20Knows%20Best%E2%80%9D%20and