in%20August%202020.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnToday%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20connectivity%20has%20improved%20--%20inside%20and%20out.%20%26quot%3BRail%20and%20road%20connectivity%20are%20being%20enhanced..%20air%20connectivity%20to%20Jammu%20has%20improved...%20the%20Union%20Territory%20has%20ranked%20third%20in%20PM%20Gram%20Sadak%20Yojana%2C%20with%20six%20to%2020%20km%20of%20road%20being%20built%20daily...%20Power%20was%20a%20big%20issue%20but%20in%203.5%20years%2C%20electricity%20production%20will%20be%20doubled%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMassive%20strides%20are%20also%20being%20made%20in%20getting%20piped%20water%20to%20every%20house.%20On%20the%20health%20front%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20is%20performing%20above%20the%20national%20average%2C%20he%20said%2C%20with%20%26quot%3Bnew%20AIIMS%2C%20cancer%20institutes%2C%20medical%20colleges%20coming%20up%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Centre's%20new%20industrial%20scheme%2C%20projects%20worth%20over%20Rs%2026%2C000%20crore%20are%20on%20the%20ground%20today.%20He%20said%20he%20was%20confident%20that%20over%20%26quot%3B75%2C000%20crore%20worth%20of%20investment%20will%20flow%20in%2C%20creating%20over%205%20lakh%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20has%20now%20changed%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20are%20no%20more%20shutdowns%20in%20the%20valley%20and%20no%20one%20responds%20to%20calls%20from%20across%20the%20border%E2%80%A6%20stone%20pelting%20protests%20have%20become%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20%26quot%3Blate%20night%20jam%20sessions%26quot%3B%20along%20the%20Jhelum%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20which%20has%20become%20a%20%26quot%3Bsymbol%20of%20urban%20transformation%26quot%3B%20under%20the%20Smart%20City%20Project%2C%20Mr%20Sinha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20why%20this%20is%20working%2C%20Mr%20Sinha%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20suffered%20because%20of%20terrorism...%20generations%20have%20been%20destroyed%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20has%20set%20off%20a%20huge%20boost%20in%20tourism.%20In%202022%2C%201.88%20crore%20people%20visited%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20%E2%80%93%20the%20largest%20number%20since%20Independence.%20Till%20July%20this%20year%2C%20Kashmir%20has%20seen%201.27%20crore%20footfalls%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692030480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fjn8edppo_jk-lt-gov-manoj-sinha-_625x300_14_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fscrapping-of-article-370-a-historic-moment-j-k-lt-governor-to-ndtv-4298069%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Manoj%20Sinha%2C%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20has%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20scrapping%20of%20special%20status%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20and%20moving%20it%20to%20mainstream%20has%20brought%20about%20a%20host%20of%20positive%20changes%20over%20the%20last%20four%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fscrapping-of-article-370-a-historic-moment-j-k-lt-governor-to-ndtv-4298069%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fscrapping-of-article-370-a-historic-moment-j-k-lt-governor-to-ndtv-4298069%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fscrapping-of-article-370-a-historic-moment-j-k-lt-governor-to-ndtv-4298069%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ingrid%20Ciprian-Matthews%20Takes%20Direct%20Oversight%20of%20CBS%20News%20in%20Restructure%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692030443000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F2062118_0135b.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235695716%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ingrid%20Ciprian-Matthews%20wil