d%20to%20students%20to%20%26quot%3Bnot%20entertain%20suicidal%20thoughts%20but%20to%20have%20self-confidence%20and%20to%20live%20life%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20assured%20that%20NEET%20would%20be%20gone.%20A%20bill%20seeking%20to%20exempt%20Tamil%20Nadu%20from%20NEET%20is%20pending%20the%20President's%20sign-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernor%20RN%20Ravi%2C%20who%20had%20returned%20the%20bill%20after%20a%20long%20delay%2C%20forwarded%20it%20to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20after%20the%20assembly%20passed%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Stalin%20declared%20that%20he%20would%20skip%20the%20Governor's%20traditional%20tea%20on%20Independence%20Day%20because%20of%20his%20stand%20on%20NEET.%20During%20an%20interaction%20with%20NEET%20toppers%2C%20the%20governor%20had%20reportedly%20said%20he%20would%20never%20sign%20the%20state%20government's%20bill%2C%20even%20if%20he%20had%20the%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20I%20will%20be%20the%20last%20man%20to%20give%20clearance%3B%20never%2C%20ever.%20I%20do%20not%20want%20my%20children%20to%20feel%20intellectually%20disabled.%20I%20want%20our%20children%20to%20compete%20and%20be%20the%20best.%20They%20have%20proved%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20double%20tragedy%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20wrote%20to%20President%20Murmu%20requesting%20her%20to%20clear%20the%20bill.%20The%20death%20count%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20due%20to%20student%20suicides%20over%20NEET%20stands%20at%2016%2C%20he%20told%20the%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStudent%20suicides%20could%20have%20been%20avoided%20if%20our%20Bill%20for%20exemption%20from%20NEET%20was%20given%20assent%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Stalin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEach%20day%20of%20delay%20in%20its%20implementation%20costs%20not%20only%20valuable%20medical%20seats%20to%20deserving%20students%20but%20invaluable%20human%20lives%20to%20our%20society.%20I%2C%20therefore%2C%20solicit%20your%20immediate%20intervention