3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14172438%2Feviction-pic-2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22962%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14172438%2Feviction-pic-2.jpg%20962w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14172438%2Feviction-pic-2-300x231.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668071%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22741%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJesmina%20Khatun.%20Photo%3A%20Nazimuddin%20Siddique%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20eviction%2C%20the%20victims%20had%20no%20place%20to%20go%2C%20and%20they%20end%20up%20taking%20shelter%20on%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20village%20roads.%20The%20administration%20also%20removed%20them%20from%20the%20village%20roads.%20They%20survived%20with%20%3Cem%3EChira-%20Muri%20%3C%2Fem%3E(flattened%20rice-puffed%20rice)%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20three%20days%20without%20food.%20They%20did%20not%20have%20even%20water%20to%20drink.%20This%20author%20saw%20them%20drinking%20water%20from%20dirty%20ponds.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20long%20before%20another%20brutal%20eviction%20was%20carried%20out%20against%2047%20families%20in%20the%20Satra%20Kanra%20area%20of%20Baghbar%2C%20Barpeta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20%E2%80%98criminal%E2%80%99%20eviction%20drives%20have%20been%20continuing%20in%20different%20places.%20What%20do%20these%20evictions%20all%20have%20in%20common%3F%20They%20are%20against%20Miya%20Muslims%20who%20moved%20from%20erstwhile%20Bengal.%20Instead%20of%20solving%20the%20underlying%20problems%20of%20poverty%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20in%20the%20state%20has%20been%20using%20disproportionate%20force%20and%20targeted%20threats%20against%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesnownews.com%2Fvideos%2Fmirror-now%2Fsociety%2Fmassive-eviction-drive-against-illegal-immigrants-in-assam-video-96348994%5C%22%3Eillegal%20encroachers%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9C.%20While%20the%20homes%20of%20Muslims%20are%20selectively%20demolished%2C%20in%20reality%2C%20landless%20people%20belonging%20to%20different%20tribes%2C%20religions%2C%20and%20linguistic%20groups%20have%20been%20living%20on%20government%20lands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%20in%20the%20Bodoland%20Territorial%20Region%20(BTR)%2C%20an%20autonomous%20council%20of%20Assam%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20eviction%20notices%20were%20selectively%20issued%20predominantly%20to%20Muslims%20in%20several%20areas%20of%20different%20districts.%20These%20include%20Hasraobari%2C%20Mauzabari%2C%20Donshiapara%20of%20Chirang%20district%2C%20and%20Nk%20Darranga%20of%20Tamulpur%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20509px)%2085vw%2C%20509px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14172605%2FDoc.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22509%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14172605%2FDoc.jpg%20509w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14172605%2FDoc-212x300.jpg%20212w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668073%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EList%20of%20people%20who%20were%20served%20eviction%20notices%20in%20Tamulpur%20district%2C%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOsman%20Ali%20from%20the%20village%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20living%20in%20the%20village%20for%20over%20100%20years%2C%20and%20the%20government%20has%20put%20a%20notice%20in%20our%20local%20market%20to%20vacate%20our%20land.%20Though%20our%20land%20is%20in%20a%20tribal%20belt%20and%20block%20area%2C%20there%20are%20other%20communities%20too%20in%20this%20protected%20belt%20and%20block%2C%20including%20Bengali