ang-eviction-drive-government%5C%22%3EAssam%20Firing%3A%20What%20Happened%20During%20the%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Eviction%20Drive%20in%20Darrang%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20the%20unabated%20destruction%20of%20homes%20is%20the%20newest%20development%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-quotes-amrit-kaal-14-times-in-august-15-speech-3264575%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Amrit%20Kaal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%99%20the%20new%20slogan%20to%20describe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Famrit-kaal-meaning-origin-explained-union-budget-2022%5C%22%3EModi%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fa%3E%20vision%20of%20%E2%80%98100%25%20development%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98New%20India%E2%80%99.%20The%20government%20is%20celebrating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Famritmahotsav.nic.in%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Azadi%20ka%20Amrit%20Mahotsav%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20the%20country%20is%20going%20to%20celebrate%20another%20Independence%20Day%2C%20thousands%20of%20%3Cem%3EMiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20Muslims%20have%20been%20left%20in%20a%20state%20of%20limbo%20%E2%80%93%20without%20a%20piece%20of%20land%2C%20a%20home%2C%20and%20a%20future.%20Some%20more%20have%20received%20eviction%20notices%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20Assam.%20These%20targeted%20evictions%20are%20not%20only%20against%20humanity%20but%20also%20against%20Article%2023-24%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%2C%20which%20guarantees%20fundamental%20rights%20against%20exploitation.%20The%20preamble%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20guarantees%20equality%20and%20individual%20dignity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20clear%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98threat%E2%80%99%20they%20pose%20is%20not%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20encroachment%E2%80%9D%20on%20land%20or%20public%20resources.%20If%20the%20government%20can%20allot%20lands%20to%20controversial%20Indian%20yoga%20guru%20turned%20businessman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Finvestigates%2Fspecial-report%2Findia-modi-ramdev%2F%5C%22%3EBaba%20Ramdev%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20to%20owners%20of%20private%20enterprises%2C%20including%20tea%20gardens%2C%20why%20can%20it%20not%20give%20land%20to%20the%20poor%20citizens%20of%20the%20country%20just%20to%20survive%3F%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcag.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fdownload_audit_report%2F2022%2FReport-No.-4-of-2022_English-063aa92eb7e3732.33325568.pdf%5C%22%3EAuditor%20General%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereported%2C%20are%20993%20police%20officers%20illegally%20living%20in%20government%20housing%20%E2%80%93%20probably%20the%20very%20same%20officers%20who%20are%20evicting%20families%20such%20as%20Jesmina%E2%80%99s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20questions%2C%20like%20%3Cem%3EMiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20Muslims%E2%80%99%20homes%2C%20are%20squashed%20in%20the%20public%20sphere.%20The%20%3Cem%3Egodi-%3C%2Fem%3Emedia%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1040558%2Fwhy-eviction-drives-in-assam-are-no-longer-facing-resistance%5C%22%3Efalsely%20terms%3C%2Fa%3E%20innocent%20families%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigrants%E2%80%9D%2C%20aligning%20with%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20violent%20campaign%20to%20remove%20citizenship%20rights%20in%20the%20violent%20project%20of%20building%20a%20Hindu%20Rashtra.%20When%20the%20international%20media%20revealed%20this%20agenda%20in%20a%20recent%20BBC%20documentary%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Modi%20Question%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20video%20was%20banned%2C%20and%20those%20who%20attended%20screenings%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-asia-india-64407921%5C%22%3Edetained.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20families%20who%20face%20the%20brunt%20of%20this%20violent%20agenda%20are%20doing%20so%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20unheard%2C%20with%20no%20medium%20to%20tell%20their%20stories%20of%20extreme%20sorrow%20to%20the%20international%20community%2C%20let%20alone%20their%20fellow%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20post-colonial%20Assam%2C%20Muslims%2C%20especially%20the%20Miya%20Muslims%2C%20have%20always%20been%20on%20the%20margin%20and%20under%20systematic%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fassam-nrc-a-history-of-violence-and-persecution%5C%22%3Epersecution%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Especially%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20power%20in%20Assam%2C%20the%20government%20has%20been%20using%20various%20mechanisms%20such%20as%20%E2%80%98Doubtful-voter%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20to%20harass%20the%20Miya%20community.%20Recently%2C%20the%20government%20of%20Assam%20has%20started%20utilising%20the%20eviction%20tool%20to%20make%20the%20people%20homeless%2C%20landless%2C%20jobless%2C%20and%20to%20strip%20them%20of%20their%20citizenship%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20the%20government%20came%20out%20with%20the%20idea%20to%20arrest%20people%20in%20the%20name%20of%20child%20marriage%2C%20and%20hundreds%20of%20youth%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F03%2F10%2Findia-assam-child-underage-marriage%2F%5C%22%3Ewere%20arrested%20from%20the%20marginalised%20community%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Such%20exclusionary%20mechanism%20of%20the%20government%20of%20Assam%20finds%20resonance%20in%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20as%20well%20as%20the%20BJP%20governments%20of%20various%20other%20states%2C%20including%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20(currently%20under%20President%E2%80%99s%20rule).%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20central%20government%20is%20known%20for%20its%20anti-Muslim%20policies%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20and%20revocation%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20and%20down-gradation%20of%20the%20statehood%20of%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20landless%20people%20is%20growing%20thanks%20to%20annual%20floods%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsoil-erosion-has-left-nearly-90000-landless-in-assam-in-l