2https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-president-alvi-calls-for-unity-amidst-76th-independence-day-celebrations%2Famp_articleshow%2F102721910.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-president-alvi-calls-for-unity-amidst-76th-independence-day-celebrations%2Famp_articleshow%2F102721910.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RBI%20to%20Use%20AI%20for%20Regulatory%20Supervision%2C%20Awards%20Contract%20to%20McKinsey%20and%20Accenture%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Frbi_pti.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20will%20work%20with%20global%20consultancy%20firms%20McKinsey%20and%20Accenture%20to%20improve%20its%20regulatory%20supervision%20over%20banks%20and%20Non-Banking%20Financial%20Corporations%20(NBFCs)%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20and%20machine%20learning%20(ML).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyourstory.com%2F2023%2F08%2Frbi-selects-mckinsey-accenture-ml-ai%5C%22%3EPTI%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9CRBI%20is%20looking%20to%20use%20advanced%20analytics%2C%20AI%2C%20and%20ML%20to%20analyse%20its%20huge%20database%20and%20improve%20regulatory%20supervision%20over%20banks%20and%20NBFCs.%20For%20this%20purpose%2C%20the%20central%20bank%20plans%20to%20hire%20experts%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%20last%20year%2C%20the%20central%20bank%20had%20invited%20the%20expression%20of%20interest%20(EoI)%20from%20firms%20to%20be%20engaged%20as%20consultants%20to%20help%20RBI%20by%20generating%20supervisory%20inputs.%20Seven%20were%20shortlisted%20among%20the%20applicants%2C%20namely%20Accenture%20Solutions%20Private%20Limited%2C%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group%20(India)%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20Deloitte%20Touche%20Tohmatsu%20India%20LLP%2C%20Ernst%20and%20Young%20LLP%2C%20KPMG%20Assurance%20and%20Consulting%20Services%20LLP%2C%20McKinsey%20and%20Company%2C%20and%20Pricewaterhouse%20Coopers%20Pvt%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20RBI%20has%20zeroed%20in%20on%20McKinsey%20and%20Company%2C%20and%20Accenture%20Solutions%20Private%20Limited.%20The%20project%20is%20set%20to%20cost%20Rs%2091%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20RBI%20has%20already%20been%20using%20AI%20and%20ML%20in%20its%20supervisory%20processes%2C%20it%20now%20intends%20to%20scale%20it%20up%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20benefits%20of%20advanced%20analytics%C2%A0can%20accrue%20to%20the%20Department%20of%20Supervision%20in%20the%20central%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20RBI%20in%20September%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Supervision%20had%20already%20been%20developing%20and%20using%20linear%20and%20a%20few%20machine-learning%20models%20for%20supervisory%20examinations.%20But%2C%20it%20said%20the%20interest%20now%20is%20to%20explore%20the%20data%20to%20identify%20its%20attributes%20that%20can%20be%20leveraged%20to%20generate%20new%20and%20improved%20supervisory%20inputs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanks%2C%20urban%20cooperative%20banks%2C%20NBFCs%2C%20payment%20banks%2C%20small%20finance%20banks%2C%20local%20area%20banks%2C%20credit%20information%20companies%2C%20and%20select%20all%20Indian%20financial%20institutions%20come%20under%20the%20supervisory%20ambit%20of%20the%20RBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20supervision%2C%20RBI%20assesses%20the%20financial%20soundness%2C%20solvency%2C%20asset%20quality%2C%20governance%20framework%2C%20liquidity%2C%20and%20operational%20viability%20of%20these%20institutions%20to%20save%20depositors%E2%80%99%20interests%20and%20financial%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%2C%20in%20its%20EoI%20issued%20in%20September%20last%20year%2C%20had%20said%20regulatory%20and%20supervisory%20authorities%20around%20the%20globe%20are%20using%20machine%20learning%20te