%20due%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20new%20Bills%20have%20Hindi%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20new%20bills%20are%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20which%20will%20replace%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%201860%3B%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20Bill%2C%202023%20which%20will%20replace%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%2C%201898%3B%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Bill%2C%202023%20which%20will%20replace%20the%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%2C%201872.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%2C%20while%20Shah%20said%20in%20parliament%20that%20the%20government%20will%20%E2%80%9Crepeal%20sedition%20completely%2C%E2%80%9D%20only%20the%20word%20has%20been%20removed%2C%20not%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurjewala%20has%20said%20that%20mob%20lynching%20was%20earlier%20covered%20under%20Section%20302%20(murder)%20of%20IPC%20in%20which%20death%20penalty%20or%20life%20imprisonment%20were%20the%20punishments.%20Now%2C%20Surjewala%20said%2C%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20government%20was%20giving%20huge%20%E2%80%9Cconcessions%E2%80%9D%20to%20those%20accused%20of%20lynching%20by%20watering%20down%20the%20lowest%20punishment%20to%20seven%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurjewala%20also%20said%20that%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20claim%20in%20parliament%20that%20hate%20speech%20would%20be%20penalised%20under%20the%20new%20Bills%20is%20also%20false%20as%20there%20were%20provisions%20in%20the%20IPC%20under%20which%20it%20was%20already%20covered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurjewala%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EHerald%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20also%20alleged%20that%20Shah%20%E2%80%9Clied%20%5Bto%5D%20and%20misled%E2%80%9D%20the%20parliament%20on%20%E2%80%98zero%20FIRs%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98e-FIRs%E2%80%99%2C%20both%20of%20which%20were%20launched%20by%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20government%20under%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20the%20mandatory%20video%20recording%20of%20a%20rape%20victim%E2%80%99s%20statement%20has%20now%20been%20made%20optional%20under%20the%20changes%20introduced%20by%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurjewala%20also%20said%20that%20punishment%20for%20terrorist%20acts%20and%20other%20crimes%20were%20also%20falsely%20advertised%20by%20Shah%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692001380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25203412%2FScreenshot-2023-07-25-at-8.33.25-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Famit-shah-misled-parliament-on-three-criminal-bills-congress%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20has%20said%20that%20the%20Union%20home%20minister's%20claim%20that%20the%20new%20Bills%20are%20tough%20on%20crimes%20like%20mob%20lynching%20and%20hate%20speech%20are%20false.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Famit-shah-misled-parliament-on-three-criminal-bills-congress%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22FC%20Bayern%20Condemns%20Racist%20Abuse%20of%20Striker%20Mathys%20Tel%20at%20Super%20Cup%20Match%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14133655%2FMathys-Tel-in-2022.png%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBundesliga%C2%A0champions%C2%A0Bayern%20Munich%C2%A0on%20Sunday%20strongly%20condemned%20%E2%80%9Cinhumane%E2%80%9D%C2%A0racist%20abuse%C2%A0received%20by%20striker%20Mathys%20Tel%20after%20the%20team%E2%80%99s%20Super%20Cup%20match%20against%20RB%20Leipzig.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2018-year-old%20French%20striker%20started%20Saturday%E2%80%99s%20game%20at%20the%20Allianz%20Arena%C2%A0but%C2%A0missed%20several%20chances%20for%20Bayern%20and%20was%20replaced%20after%2064%20minutes%20by%20newly-signed%20England%20striker%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%