about%20their%20Tinder%20issues%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20stepped%20into%20comedy%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20tell%20them%20that%20I%20was%20from%20Bhayandar.%20But%20then%20the%20more%20I%20delved%20into%20my%20queer%20self%2C%20the%20more%20I%20realised%20that%20this%20is%20my%20reality.%20I%20was%20born%20in%20a%20chawl%20and%20I%20did%20have%20to%20take%20a%20bucket%20to%20a%20common%20toilet%20stall%20every%20morning.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20reality%20of%20so%20many%20people%20in%20the%20city.%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20deny%20it.%20The%20more%20I%20owned%20up%20to%20that%20reality%2C%20the%20onus%20was%20on%20me%20to%20be%20truthful%20as%20well%20as%20funny%20by%20tagging%20a%20punch%20line%20at%20the%20end%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCvbqq6soJdD%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCvbqq6soJdD%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCvbqq6soJdD%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Navin%20Noronha%20(%40houseofnoronha)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Apne%20mein%20chalta%20hai%2C%20bahar%20jaake%20mat%20karna%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20recent%20special%20%E2%80%98The%20Good%20Child%E2%80%99%2C%20Navin%20narrates%20a%20hilarious%20story%20from%20his%20childhood%20growing%20up%20in%20a%20chawl%20in%20Golibar%20road.%20In%20this%20particular%20segment%2C%20he%20recalled%20how%20there%20were%20just%20five%20common%20toilets%20for%20hundreds%20of%20families%20living%20in%20his%20chawl.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20one%20morning%20as%20a%20five-year-old%2C%20Navin%20stepped%20out%20with%20a%20bucket%20of%20water%20and%20walked%20towards%20the%20common%20toilet%20stalls%20to%20do%20his%20business.%20Unable%20to%20control%20his%20bowels%2C%20however%2C%20he%20released%20portions%20of%20his%20excrement%20along%20the%20passageway.%20Later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20a%20collection%20of%2010%20neighbourhood%20aunties%20stood%20outside%20his%20home%20complaining%20to%20his%20mother%20about%20what%20he%20did.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20hilariously%20denying%20his%20son%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20in%20the%20crime%2C%20Navin%E2%80%99s%20mother%20tells%20him%20something%20that%20he%20would%20hear%20again%20years%20later%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CApne%20mein%20chalta%20hai%2C%20bahar%20jaake%20mat%20karna%3C%2Fem%3E%20(do%20whatever%20you%20want%20within%20the%20confines%20of%20your%20private%20space%2C%20just%20don%E2%80%99t%20do%20it%20outside)%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYears%20later%2C%20when%20he%20finally%20found%20the%20courage%20to%20come%20out%20and%20introduce%20his%20partner%20to%20his%20mother%20at%2027%2C%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20reject%20his%20queer%20identity%2C%20but%20did%20say%20one%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20%3